00:00:01,660 --> 00:00:10,080
EnglishPod.com Good afternoon, passport and arrival card please.

2
00:00:10,439 --> 00:00:11,060
Here you are.

3
00:00:11,439 --> 00:00:12,279
Where are you coming from?

4
00:00:12,560 --> 00:00:12,740
China.

5
00:00:13,339 --> 00:00:14,859
Is this your country of birth or residence?

6
00:00:15,160 --> 00:00:15,980
I just work there.

7
00:00:16,660 --> 00:00:18,800
What is the purpose of your visit to the United States?

8
00:00:19,019 --> 00:00:19,920
I'm here on vacation.

9
00:00:20,620 --> 00:00:22,739
How long do you plan to stay in the United States?

10
00:00:23,039 --> 00:00:24,100
Almost three weeks.

11
00:00:24,780 --> 00:00:28,719
Sir, you didn't fill out the information on your arrival card of where you'll be staying.

12
00:00:29,359 --> 00:00:34,719
Oh, I'm sorry, but there are a couple different places I will travel to within the United States, so I wasn't sure what to put.

13
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:38,659
You must specify an address on the place where you will spend most of your time.

14
00:00:38,920 --> 00:00:39,219
Okay.

15
00:00:42,479 --> 00:00:43,399
Here you are.

16
00:00:43,920 --> 00:00:46,420
Do you have enough means to support yourself while you're here?

17
00:00:46,679 --> 00:00:49,000
Yes, I have some traveler's checks and two credit cards.

18
00:00:49,500 --> 00:00:49,859
Very good.

19
00:00:50,280 --> 00:00:51,399
Do you have anything to declare?

20
00:00:51,759 --> 00:00:53,820
Nope, I only have my clothes and camera.

21
00:00:54,299 --> 00:00:54,899
Very well, sir.

22
00:00:55,340 --> 00:00:56,600
Welcome to the United States.

23
00:00:57,020 --> 00:00:57,679
Enjoy your visit.

